1
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:08,274
( thunder crashing )

2
00:00:08,341 --> 00:00:09,510
( man laughs )

3
00:00:09,576 --> 00:00:12,646
FEAST YOUR EYES ON THAT WRECK,
WOULD YA?

4
00:00:12,679 --> 00:00:14,615
♪

5
00:00:18,752 --> 00:00:20,086
DAMNATION.

6
00:00:20,153 --> 00:00:22,523
( laughs )

7
00:00:22,589 --> 00:00:24,791
THIS BASTARD MUST'VE DIED
RIGHT QUICKLIKE.

8
00:00:24,858 --> 00:00:27,327
FELL OFF THAT CLIFF,
I'LL WARRANT.

9
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:29,462
CARRIAGE WHEELS
SLIPPED IN THE MUD.

10
00:00:29,530 --> 00:00:31,197
THEY WEREN'T HURTING FOR COIN,

11
00:00:31,264 --> 00:00:33,366
IF THESE FINE CLOTHES
TELL IT TRUE.

12
00:00:33,433 --> 00:00:34,535
‐ ( baby crying )
‐ Woman: DARIO!

13
00:00:34,635 --> 00:00:37,370
THE LADY IS DEAD,
BUT THE BABY WITH HER,

14
00:00:37,470 --> 00:00:39,472
IT'S STILL ALIVE.
I CAN HEAR IT.

15
00:00:39,540 --> 00:00:41,775
SHE MUST HAVE PROTECTED IT
WITH HER BODY.

16
00:00:41,842 --> 00:00:45,045
Dario: LEAVE IT BE.
SOON ENOUGH, IT'LL BE DEAD.

17
00:00:45,145 --> 00:00:47,648
Woman: W‐WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

18
00:00:47,714 --> 00:00:49,783
Dario: YOU'VE GOT EYES,
AIN'T YA, WOMAN?

19
00:00:49,850 --> 00:00:52,218
I'M APPROPRIATING HIS JEWELRY.

20
00:00:52,285 --> 00:00:54,955
EH? WHAT HAVE WE HERE?

21
00:00:56,523 --> 00:00:59,392
EVIL‐LOOKING THING, AIN'T IT?

22
00:00:59,492 --> 00:01:01,067
WON'T FETCH ME NOTHIN'.

23
00:01:01,134 --> 00:01:02,836
HEY! LEND A HAND!

24
00:01:02,903 --> 00:01:05,405
HELP ME YANK OUT
HIS PEARLY TEETH!

25
00:01:05,471 --> 00:01:07,007
THEY'LL FETCH A PRETTY COPPER.

26
00:01:07,073 --> 00:01:08,174
EH? WHA?!

27
00:01:08,241 --> 00:01:12,846
Man: PROVIDENCE SENDS ME AID
IN THE GUISE OF A MAN.

28
00:01:12,913 --> 00:01:13,914
MANY THANKS.

29
00:01:14,014 --> 00:01:15,081
Dario: EH?

30
00:01:15,148 --> 00:01:16,416
Man: MY WIFE...

31
00:01:16,517 --> 00:01:19,019
MY WIFE AND SON,

32
00:01:19,085 --> 00:01:20,554
TELL ME, DO THEY LIVE?

33
00:01:20,587 --> 00:01:22,556
Dario: I HATE TO SAY IT,

34
00:01:22,589 --> 00:01:24,558
BUT YOUR WIFE,
SAINTS PRESERVE HER,

35
00:01:24,591 --> 00:01:26,827
HAS GONE ON
TO HER HEAVENLY REST,

36
00:01:26,893 --> 00:01:29,763
BUT THE BABY IS ALIVE AND WELL.

37
00:01:29,863 --> 00:01:31,164
( man sighs )

38
00:01:31,231 --> 00:01:34,367
FATE IS MOST CRUEL.

39
00:01:34,434 --> 00:01:37,070
MY NAME IS GEORGE JOESTAR.

40
00:01:37,103 --> 00:01:40,674
YOU HAVE SAVED MY LIFE
THIS CURSED NIGHT.

41
00:01:40,741 --> 00:01:42,442
QUICKLY TELL ME YOUR NAME,

42
00:01:42,543 --> 00:01:45,779
THAT I MAY REMEMBER
BEFORE MY SENSES FAIL ME.

43
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:46,947
( gasps )

44
00:01:47,047 --> 00:01:48,882
( Dario thinking )
THIS PEACOCK THINKS I'M HERE

45
00:01:48,949 --> 00:01:50,584
OUTTA THE GOODNESS OF ME HEART.

46
00:01:50,617 --> 00:01:52,919
HEH HEH HEH HEH HEH.
LITTLE DOES HE KNOW.

47
00:01:52,953 --> 00:01:55,455
HA HA HA HA!
GUESS I'LL OBLIGE HIM!

48
00:01:55,556 --> 00:01:58,391
DARIO BRANDO, YOUR LORDSHIP.

49
00:01:58,458 --> 00:02:00,694
George: SIR, I SWEAR TO YOU,

50
00:02:00,761 --> 00:02:05,939
THE JOESTAR FAMILY WILL HONOR
THE DEBT WE HAVE INCURRED.

51
00:02:08,875 --> 00:02:10,811
♪

52
00:02:16,916 --> 00:02:17,884
( dog barks )

53
00:02:17,951 --> 00:02:20,654
Boy: AH, THERE'S A GOOD BOY.

54
00:02:20,754 --> 00:02:22,823
FATHER! I'M OFF!

55
00:02:22,889 --> 00:02:24,825
George:
THEN FARE THEE WELL, JOJO!

56
00:02:24,891 --> 00:02:27,060
‐ JoJo: LET'S GO, DANNY!
‐ ( Danny barks )

57
00:02:27,127 --> 00:02:29,062
♪

58
00:02:34,300 --> 00:02:37,003
( man coughs )

59
00:02:37,070 --> 00:02:38,505
DIO.

60
00:02:38,572 --> 00:02:40,106
( coughs )

61
00:02:40,173 --> 00:02:41,341
MIND YOUR FATHER.

62
00:02:41,407 --> 00:02:43,343
( coughs )

63
00:02:43,443 --> 00:02:45,345
DAMN YOUR EYES, YOU LAZY BOY.

64
00:02:45,445 --> 00:02:46,680
ARE YOU DEAF?

65
00:02:48,248 --> 00:02:50,016
( Dio sighs )

66
00:02:50,083 --> 00:02:51,852
WHAT DO YOU WANT,
FATHER, MEDICINE?

67
00:02:51,952 --> 00:02:54,955
Dario: YOU IDIOT!
THEIR SNAKE OIL DOES ME NO GOOD.

68
00:02:55,021 --> 00:02:56,657
GET OUT OF HERE,
AND DON'T COME BACK

69
00:02:56,690 --> 00:02:59,693
UNTIL YOU'VE
FOUND ME SOME BOOZE!

70
00:02:59,793 --> 00:03:01,702
♪

71
00:03:05,872 --> 00:03:07,841
George: YOUR MANNERS
ARE DREADFUL.

72
00:03:08,875 --> 00:03:10,476
JoJo: FORGIVE ME, FATHER.

73
00:03:10,544 --> 00:03:13,046
‐ Dio: CHECKMATE.
‐ ( man growls )

74
00:03:15,448 --> 00:03:16,617
TAKE IT.

75
00:03:21,555 --> 00:03:24,324
DON'T FEEL SO SMART NOW,
DO YA, WHELP?

76
00:03:24,390 --> 00:03:27,493
( Dio gasps )

77
00:03:27,561 --> 00:03:29,195
‐ ( boys laughing )
‐ Girl: NO, STOP!

78
00:03:29,229 --> 00:03:30,897
‐ PLEASE, JUST GIVE HER BACK!
‐ Boy: YEAH! YEAH!

79
00:03:30,997 --> 00:03:32,733
Boy #2: OH, LEMME GUESS, ERINA!

80
00:03:32,799 --> 00:03:34,234
YOUR DADDY BOUGHT YOU
THIS DOLL, DIDN'T HE?

81
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:38,238
IT'S FANCY. BEING A QUACK
MUST PAY HIM REAL NICE.

82
00:03:38,304 --> 00:03:39,906
I KNOW.

83
00:03:39,973 --> 00:03:43,076
WHAT DO YA SAY WE PEEL OFF
THIS FANCY‐LOOKING DRESS, EH,

84
00:03:43,176 --> 00:03:44,578
AND SEE IF THEY MADE HER

85
00:03:44,678 --> 00:03:46,713
WITH ALL
THE REAL GIRL BITS UNDERNEATH?

86
00:03:48,048 --> 00:03:50,717
‐ ( Erina crying )
‐ ( boys laughing )

87
00:03:50,751 --> 00:03:54,087
ERINA'S A CRYBABY!
ERINA'S A CRYBABY!

88
00:03:54,187 --> 00:03:56,322
‐ ERINA'S A CRY‐‐
‐ JoJo: THAT'S ENOUGH!

89
00:03:56,389 --> 00:03:58,258
GIVE IT BACK TO HER RIGHT NOW!

90
00:03:58,358 --> 00:03:59,492
Boy #2: WHO'S THIS GUY?

91
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,334
Boy #1: YOU SOME FRIEND
OF ERINA'S?

92
00:04:01,401 --> 00:04:02,536
JoJo: I'VE NEVER MET HER,

93
00:04:02,603 --> 00:04:04,237
BUT I'LL FIGHT FOR HER
ALL THE SAME!

94
00:04:05,939 --> 00:04:07,207
Boy #1: WHO IS THIS IDIOT?

95
00:04:07,273 --> 00:04:10,210
GETTING IN A FIGHT
FOR A GIRL HE DON'T EVEN KNOW!

96
00:04:10,276 --> 00:04:11,211
( JoJo gasps )

97
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:16,016
Boy #2: LOOKS LIKE SOMEBODY
WAS NOTHIN' BUT TALK.

98
00:04:16,082 --> 00:04:17,684
( both laugh )

99
00:04:17,751 --> 00:04:19,786
Boy #1: LOOK AT HIM
THERE ON THE GROUND.

100
00:04:19,853 --> 00:04:21,187
ARE YOU GONNA CRY?

101
00:04:21,254 --> 00:04:24,290
SOME KNIGHT IN SHINING ARMOR
YOU TURNED OUT TO BE.

102
00:04:24,357 --> 00:04:26,893
( JoJo gasping )

103
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:30,697
Boy #1: HUH? THIS LITTLE
PANTYWAIST IS THE JOESTAR KID.

104
00:04:30,764 --> 00:04:33,366
NOW THAT I KNOW
YOU'RE SOME RICH GUY'S SON,

105
00:04:33,432 --> 00:04:34,534
WE'RE JUST GETTING STARTED.

106
00:04:34,601 --> 00:04:36,636
YOU CAN'T
BUY YOUR WAY OUTTA THIS.

107
00:04:36,736 --> 00:04:37,637
( blows striking )

108
00:04:37,737 --> 00:04:39,305
Boy #2: HIT HIM SOME MORE!

109
00:04:39,405 --> 00:04:43,476
Dario: LISTEN, DIO.
I AM NOT LONG FOR THIS WORLD.

110
00:04:43,577 --> 00:04:45,712
WHEN I DIE‐‐( coughs )

111
00:04:45,779 --> 00:04:48,949
YOU GET YOURSELF
TO THE JOESTAR MANSION

112
00:04:48,982 --> 00:04:50,751
ALONG WITH THIS LETTER.

113
00:04:50,817 --> 00:04:52,953
THE FOOL THINKS HE OWES ME.

114
00:04:52,986 --> 00:04:55,956
THIS IS
YOUR TICKET TO GREATNESS.

115
00:04:55,989 --> 00:04:58,792
IT'S YOUR ONLY CHANCE, DIO.
GO OUT THERE,

116
00:04:58,825 --> 00:05:02,669
AND TAKE THIS USELESS WORLD
FOR ALL YOU CAN GET.

117
00:05:02,736 --> 00:05:04,070
( JoJo groans )

118
00:05:04,137 --> 00:05:04,971
( boy #1 spits )

119
00:05:05,005 --> 00:05:06,973
CRAWL ON BACK
TO YOUR DAMN MANOR,

120
00:05:07,007 --> 00:05:08,241
LITTLE LORD FAUNTLEROY.

121
00:05:08,308 --> 00:05:09,510
Boy #2: LET'S GO.

122
00:05:09,576 --> 00:05:11,678
( JoJo groaning )

123
00:05:14,781 --> 00:05:15,682
Erina: YOU OKAY?

124
00:05:15,782 --> 00:05:17,450
JoJo: JUST LEAVE ME ALONE!

125
00:05:17,518 --> 00:05:18,785
I'LL BE FINE!

126
00:05:18,852 --> 00:05:21,688
I DID NOT TAKE A BEATING
JUST NOW FOR YOUR SAKE,

127
00:05:21,755 --> 00:05:23,824
SO WHATEVER
YOU'RE THINKING, STOP IT!

128
00:05:23,857 --> 00:05:27,093
ALL I WANT IS TO CONDUCT MYSELF
AS A GENTLEMAN.

129
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:29,830
I SPOTTED A DAMSEL IN DISTRESS.

130
00:05:29,863 --> 00:05:31,832
A TRUE GENTLEMAN HAS NO FEAR.

131
00:05:31,865 --> 00:05:33,433
HE'LL FIGHT FOR THOSE WHO CAN'T.

132
00:05:33,499 --> 00:05:36,537
EVEN KNOWING IT'S A FIGHT
HE HAS NO CHANCE OF WINNING,

133
00:05:36,637 --> 00:05:38,004
HE ENTERS THE FRAY.

134
00:05:39,272 --> 00:05:43,343
SOMEDAY, I'LL HAVE
THE STRENGTH TO WIN.

135
00:05:43,376 --> 00:05:45,345
( bird squawking )

136
00:05:46,813 --> 00:05:48,014
Dio: DEVIL THAT YOU WERE,

137
00:05:48,048 --> 00:05:49,950
YOU DROVE MOTHER
TO AN EARLY GRAVE.

138
00:05:50,016 --> 00:05:51,351
I'M GLAD YOU'RE DEAD.

139
00:05:51,384 --> 00:05:53,153
MAY YOU BURN FOR YOUR SINS.

140
00:05:53,219 --> 00:05:55,656
THE RICHES
THAT ELUDED YOUR GRASP,

141
00:05:55,722 --> 00:05:57,457
I WILL CLAIM THEM IN EXCESS.

142
00:05:57,524 --> 00:05:59,893
YOU LACKED THE CUNNING
TO TAKE WHAT YOU WANTED,

143
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:02,135
BUT I'LL PREVAIL.

144
00:06:02,202 --> 00:06:04,538
THIS JOESTAR SHALL BE THE KEY.

145
00:06:04,571 --> 00:06:06,006
NOW BURN. ( spits )

146
00:06:07,508 --> 00:06:09,409
♪

147
00:06:13,079 --> 00:06:16,316
I WILL CLAIM
WHAT IS RIGHTFULLY MINE.

148
00:06:21,755 --> 00:06:25,025
Erina: "JONATHAN JOESTAR."

149
00:06:25,091 --> 00:06:27,828
Narrator: THIS IS THE TALE
OF TWO YOUNG MEN,

150
00:06:27,894 --> 00:06:30,096
THEIR DESTINIES
BOUND TO INTERSECT,

151
00:06:30,163 --> 00:06:34,167
AND THE STONE MASK THAT CHANGES
THEIR FATES FOREVER.

152
00:06:43,243 --> 00:06:45,278
( hoofbeats )

153
00:06:48,448 --> 00:06:51,117
( horses neighing )

154
00:07:04,304 --> 00:07:06,573
( chorus vocalizes )

155
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,942
( JoJo thinking ) WHO IS HE?

156
00:07:08,975 --> 00:07:11,578
YOU MUST BE DIO BRANDO, RIGHT?

157
00:07:11,645 --> 00:07:14,781
Dio: AND YOU'RE JONATHAN,
HEIR TO THE JOESTARS.

158
00:07:14,815 --> 00:07:16,783
JoJo: YES. PLEASE, CALL ME JOJO.

159
00:07:16,817 --> 00:07:18,785
IT'S A PLEASURE TO MEET YOU.

160
00:07:18,819 --> 00:07:19,820
( Danny barking )

161
00:07:19,886 --> 00:07:21,221
JoJo: DANNY!

162
00:07:21,287 --> 00:07:22,122
( laughs )

163
00:07:22,155 --> 00:07:24,224
THAT'S DANNY. HE'S MY DOG,

164
00:07:24,290 --> 00:07:26,326
AS WELL
AS MY STEADFAST COMPANION.

165
00:07:26,426 --> 00:07:29,630
DON'T WORRY. HE KNOWS BETTER
THAN TO NIP AT STRANGERS.

166
00:07:29,663 --> 00:07:31,397
( Dio scoffs )

167
00:07:31,464 --> 00:07:33,834
( Danny yelps )

168
00:07:33,934 --> 00:07:35,836
( JoJo gasps )
WHAT WAS THAT FOR?!

169
00:07:35,902 --> 00:07:37,170
HOW DARE YOU?!

170
00:07:37,237 --> 00:07:40,173
Dio: SO THIS IS
THE BRAT I MUST USURP.

171
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:43,510
WEARS HIS HEART ON HIS SLEEVE.
HE'S QUICK TO ANGER.

172
00:07:43,610 --> 00:07:47,981
THIS PAMPERED FOOL IS NO MATCH
FOR THE LIKES OF DIO BRANDO.

173
00:07:48,014 --> 00:07:48,982
George: FIGHTING ALREADY?

174
00:07:49,015 --> 00:07:50,984
( JoJo gasps )

175
00:07:51,017 --> 00:07:53,186
George: I WOULD KNOW
WHAT THIS IS ABOUT.

176
00:07:53,286 --> 00:07:55,922
Dio: SORRY.
THE DOG JUMPED AT ME,

177
00:07:55,989 --> 00:07:58,358
AND IN MY HASTE, I STRUCK IT.

178
00:07:59,459 --> 00:08:00,534
( chuckles )

179
00:08:01,635 --> 00:08:02,936
George: WELCOME TO THE MANOR.

180
00:08:03,003 --> 00:08:05,939
CONSIDER YOURSELF
A PART OF THE FAMILY.

181
00:08:06,006 --> 00:08:08,308
EVERYONE,
I WOULD HAVE DIED IN THE CRASH

182
00:08:08,374 --> 00:08:11,377
THAT CLAIMED MY WIFE
WERE IT NOT FOR DIO'S FATHER.

183
00:08:11,477 --> 00:08:14,314
YOU WILL TREAT HIM
AS YOU WOULD MY OWN SON.

184
00:08:14,380 --> 00:08:16,016
Butler: VERY WELL,
YOUR LORDSHIP.

185
00:08:16,049 --> 00:08:18,351
George: THIS IS
YOUR HOME NOW, DIO.

186
00:08:18,384 --> 00:08:21,054
PLEASE AVAIL YOURSELF
OF ALL ITS COMFORTS.

187
00:08:21,154 --> 00:08:22,388
Dio: THANK YOU, SIR,

188
00:08:22,488 --> 00:08:24,825
FOR TAKING IN
THIS POOR UNFORTUNATE.

189
00:08:24,891 --> 00:08:27,661
George: JOJO HAS LOST
HIS MOTHER AS WELL,

190
00:08:27,728 --> 00:08:29,395
AND YOU'RE THE SAME AGE.

191
00:08:29,462 --> 00:08:31,397
YOU'LL BE THICK AS THIEVES SOON.

192
00:08:31,464 --> 00:08:34,400
JOJO, DIO DIDN'T MEAN
TO HURT DANNY.

193
00:08:34,467 --> 00:08:35,201
JoJo: RIGHT.

194
00:08:35,235 --> 00:08:37,237
IT STANDS TO REASON, FATHER.

195
00:08:37,337 --> 00:08:39,740
IF A STRANGE DOG JUMPED AT ME,

196
00:08:39,806 --> 00:08:42,175
I'D BE SURPRISED, TOO.

197
00:08:42,242 --> 00:08:45,912
I WISH HIS APOLOGY
HAD BEEN MORE SINCERE,

198
00:08:46,012 --> 00:08:48,214
BUT AS WE'LL BE
LIVING HERE TOGETHER,

199
00:08:48,248 --> 00:08:50,717
I'LL DO MY UTMOST
TO BE FRIENDLY.

200
00:08:50,751 --> 00:08:51,985
George: THIS WAY, DIO.

201
00:08:52,052 --> 00:08:54,588
I'LL SHOW YOU YOUR CHAMBER.

202
00:08:54,655 --> 00:08:56,156
Dio: YES, SIR.

203
00:09:00,393 --> 00:09:02,335
( JoJo yelps )
YOU'RE HURTING ME!

204
00:09:02,402 --> 00:09:03,937
‐ PLEASE LET GO.
‐ Dio: WATCH YOUR HANDS.

205
00:09:04,004 --> 00:09:06,573
NO ONE'S ALLOWED TO TOUCH
MY THINGS WITHOUT MY PERMISSION.

206
00:09:06,607 --> 00:09:07,908
( JoJo gasps )

207
00:09:07,941 --> 00:09:11,011
Dio: NEXT TIME YOU REACH
FOR WHAT'S MINE WITH THIS PAW,

208
00:09:11,077 --> 00:09:12,012
I'LL BREAK IT.

209
00:09:12,078 --> 00:09:14,014
JoJo: I WAS ONLY TRYING TO HELP!

210
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:16,349
‐ Dio: WELL, DON'T.
‐ ( JoJo gasping )

211
00:09:16,416 --> 00:09:18,619
I WILL HAVE A SERVANT
CARRY THEM UP FOR ME.

212
00:09:20,453 --> 00:09:23,389
LISTEN. I MAY BE
A GUEST WITHIN YOUR HOUSE,

213
00:09:23,456 --> 00:09:26,126
BUT I AM NOT TO BE TRIFLED WITH.

214
00:09:26,192 --> 00:09:28,729
IN ALL THINGS THAT I DO,
I AM NUMBER ONE.

215
00:09:28,795 --> 00:09:31,464
LOOK DOWN YOUR NOSE AT ME,
AND YOU'LL REGRET IT.

216
00:09:31,532 --> 00:09:34,034
JoJo: BUT, DIO,
I WANT FOR US TO BE FRIENDS.

217
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:36,870
Dio: AND ANOTHER THING.
I HATE ALL MONGRELS.

218
00:09:36,937 --> 00:09:38,238
THEY DON'T SCARE ME.

219
00:09:38,304 --> 00:09:40,907
I JUST DESPISE HOW THEY
FAWN OVER THE UNWORTHY.

220
00:09:40,974 --> 00:09:44,811
SO KEEP THAT MANGY MUTT OF YOURS
WELL AWAY FROM ME, JOESTAR.

221
00:09:44,911 --> 00:09:47,480
George: DIO, WHAT'S KEEPING YOU?

222
00:09:47,548 --> 00:09:48,481
HURRY ALONG.

223
00:09:48,549 --> 00:09:50,050
Dio: YES, SIR.

224
00:09:51,151 --> 00:09:52,819
Narrator: WITH DIO'S
SUDDEN ARRIVAL,

225
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:57,824
JOJO'S CAREFREE LIFE
SPIRALED INTO ONE OF MISERY.

226
00:09:57,891 --> 00:09:59,159
( JoJo yelps )

227
00:09:59,259 --> 00:10:01,067
George: YOU GOT
ANOTHER ONE WRONG, JOJO!

228
00:10:01,101 --> 00:10:03,103
LOOK AT DIO. 20 OUT OF 20,

229
00:10:03,169 --> 00:10:04,437
NOT A SINGLE MISTAKE.

230
00:10:06,873 --> 00:10:08,274
( JoJo gasps )

231
00:10:08,341 --> 00:10:09,275
JOJO!

232
00:10:09,342 --> 00:10:11,244
YOUR TABLE MANNERS
ARE SIMPLY ABHORRENT.

233
00:10:11,277 --> 00:10:13,747
YOU ACT AS IF
YOU WERE RAISED IN A BARN.

234
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:15,115
( snaps fingers )

235
00:10:15,181 --> 00:10:16,416
CLEAR JOJO'S PLATE AT ONCE.

236
00:10:16,449 --> 00:10:17,951
‐ HE'S HAD ENOUGH.
‐ ( JoJo gasps )

237
00:10:18,051 --> 00:10:20,086
George: THAT'S ALL THE DINNER
YOU GET TONIGHT.

238
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:22,623
IT'S CLEAR TO ME THAT I
FAILED IN YOUR UPBRINGING

239
00:10:22,723 --> 00:10:23,857
WHEN I LOOK AT DIO.

240
00:10:23,924 --> 00:10:25,425
IF YOUR MOTHER
COULD SEE YOU NOW.

241
00:10:25,458 --> 00:10:28,595
DIO'S MANNERS ARE IMPECCABLE.

242
00:10:28,629 --> 00:10:30,731
( JoJo sighs )

243
00:10:30,797 --> 00:10:32,966
( sputtering )

244
00:10:33,867 --> 00:10:36,637
( Dio scoffs ) WHAT AN OAF.

245
00:10:36,737 --> 00:10:38,238
( men cheering )

246
00:10:38,304 --> 00:10:41,041
Host: OUR FIRST PUGILIST UP
IS JONATHAN JOESTAR.

247
00:10:41,107 --> 00:10:42,543
( crowd cheers )

248
00:10:42,609 --> 00:10:44,811
Host: HE'S BEEN LOOKING
STRONGER LATELY, I'D SAY.

249
00:10:44,911 --> 00:10:46,613
AS FOR HIS OPPONENT TODAY,

250
00:10:46,647 --> 00:10:49,282
IT'S A BOXER
WE HAVEN'T SEEN BEFORE.

251
00:10:49,315 --> 00:10:50,316
JoJo: HUH?

252
00:10:50,416 --> 00:10:52,152
Host: HE'S A NEWCOMER
TO OUR FAIR CITY.

253
00:10:52,252 --> 00:10:54,921
‐ ALL WE KNOW IS HIS NAME.
‐ Man: I WONDER HOW HE'LL DO.

254
00:10:54,988 --> 00:10:55,956
JoJo: IT CAN'T BE.

255
00:10:55,989 --> 00:10:58,258
♪

256
00:10:58,324 --> 00:11:00,667
Host: INTRODUCING
OUR SURPRISE OPPONENT,

257
00:11:00,734 --> 00:11:02,769
DIO BRANDO!

258
00:11:02,836 --> 00:11:06,006
SAME AS EVER. LAND A HIT
TO THE OTHER GUY'S FACE,

259
00:11:06,106 --> 00:11:07,974
AND THE MATCH IS OVER.
NOW FIGHT.

260
00:11:08,008 --> 00:11:08,909
‐ ( bell rings )
‐ ( crowd cheering )

261
00:11:08,975 --> 00:11:10,176
Man: GET HIM, JOJO!

262
00:11:10,243 --> 00:11:12,345
Man #2: TAKE HIM DOWN!

263
00:11:16,082 --> 00:11:18,151
Man #3: LOOK AT HIM
DODGE THOSE HITS.

264
00:11:18,184 --> 00:11:20,020
Man #1: I'VE NEVER
SEEN THE LIKE.

265
00:11:20,086 --> 00:11:21,187
JoJo: I CAN'T CONNECT.

266
00:11:21,254 --> 00:11:23,657
Dio: THE PAMPERED BRAT CAN BOX.

267
00:11:23,690 --> 00:11:24,991
I'LL GRANT HIM THAT MUCH.

268
00:11:25,025 --> 00:11:26,693
HOWEVER...

269
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:29,429
( JoJo gasps )

270
00:11:29,495 --> 00:11:31,698
Dio: HE'S NEVER
HAD TO PUNCH HIS WAY OUT

271
00:11:31,765 --> 00:11:35,435
OF A SCRAPE IN THE SLUMS,
AND THUS I HOLD THE ADVANTAGE.

272
00:11:35,502 --> 00:11:36,670
TAKE THIS.

273
00:11:36,703 --> 00:11:38,972
Host: THERE IT IS!

274
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:41,542
JOJO LOSES THE FIGHT.

275
00:11:41,608 --> 00:11:43,710
Dio: YOUR SUFFERING
ISN'T OVER YET, JOJO.

276
00:11:43,810 --> 00:11:47,313
I'LL JAM A THUMB INTO YOUR EYE
FOR GOOD MEASURE,

277
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,616
LEST YOU FORGET
WHO YOU'RE DEALING WITH.

278
00:11:53,219 --> 00:11:54,287
( crowd cheering )

279
00:11:54,354 --> 00:11:56,056
Man #2: THAT ARM
OF HIS IS UNREAL.

280
00:11:56,122 --> 00:11:57,323
Man #3: DIO!

281
00:11:57,390 --> 00:11:59,492
Man #4: DIO, THAT PUNCH
WAS SIMPLY AMAZING!

282
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:02,068
Man #1: HOW DID YOU
DODGE HIM SO WELL?

283
00:12:02,135 --> 00:12:03,870
Dio: IT'S JUST
A LITTLE DEFENSIVE FOOTWORK

284
00:12:03,904 --> 00:12:05,071
I ACQUIRED ALONG THE WAY.

285
00:12:05,138 --> 00:12:06,472
IF YOU'D LIKE TO LEARN IT,

286
00:12:06,540 --> 00:12:08,742
I'D BE MORE THAN HAPPY
TO TEACH IT TO YOU FELLAS.

287
00:12:08,842 --> 00:12:10,176
Man #1: YOU WOULD DO THAT?

288
00:12:10,243 --> 00:12:12,813
Dio: DO TAKE CARE
THAT NOBODY SHOWS IT TO JOJO.

289
00:12:12,879 --> 00:12:15,415
HE CAN'T KEEP A SECRET
TO SAVE HIS LIFE.

290
00:12:15,481 --> 00:12:16,850
Man #3: YOU DON'T SAY.

291
00:12:16,917 --> 00:12:18,251
Man #2: THANKS FOR THE WARNING.

292
00:12:18,351 --> 00:12:21,021
JoJo: THE THUMB IN MY EYE...

293
00:12:21,087 --> 00:12:22,823
THAT WAS ON PURPOSE.

294
00:12:22,889 --> 00:12:25,425
♪

295
00:12:25,491 --> 00:12:28,595
Dio: LONELINESS WILL DEVOUR
A MAN FROM WITHIN.

296
00:12:28,695 --> 00:12:31,431
I'LL REDUCE JOJO
TO AN EMPTY HUSK.

297
00:12:31,497 --> 00:12:36,202
BIT BY DEVIOUS BIT, I'LL STEAL
THE LIFE HE WAS MEANT TO HAVE.

298
00:12:36,269 --> 00:12:37,938
BY THE TIME WE'RE GROWN,

299
00:12:38,004 --> 00:12:40,273
THERE'LL BE
NOTHING LEFT OF HIM.

300
00:12:44,110 --> 00:12:45,612
♪

301
00:12:45,712 --> 00:12:47,113
JoJo: DAMN THAT DIO.

302
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:48,749
IT'S TERRIBLE.

303
00:12:48,782 --> 00:12:51,518
HE'S RUINING
EVERYTHING HE TOUCHES.

304
00:12:51,585 --> 00:12:53,787
‐ Boy: LOOK ALIVE, FELLAS.
‐ JoJo: EH?

305
00:12:53,887 --> 00:12:56,056
HEY! IT'S ME, JONATHAN!

306
00:12:56,122 --> 00:12:59,025
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!
MIND IF I JOIN YOU?!

307
00:12:59,092 --> 00:13:00,794
Boy: HUH.

308
00:13:00,894 --> 00:13:03,637
I COULD HAVE SWORN
I HEARD A VOICE A MOMENT AGO.

309
00:13:03,737 --> 00:13:06,072
Boy #2: JUST THAT SNITCH.
BETTER TO IGNORE 'EM.

310
00:13:06,139 --> 00:13:07,808
JoJo: WHAT DID YOU SAY?

311
00:13:07,874 --> 00:13:09,042
I'M A SNITCH, HUH?

312
00:13:09,109 --> 00:13:10,977
CALL ME THAT TO MY FACE!

313
00:13:11,077 --> 00:13:12,312
Boy #3: TIME TO GO.

314
00:13:12,378 --> 00:13:13,914
Boy #1: JOJO'S NOTHING
BUT A SNITCH.

315
00:13:13,980 --> 00:13:15,148
DIO WAS RIGHT ABOUT YOU.

316
00:13:15,248 --> 00:13:16,583
YOU'RE JUST A STUPID
RICH‐BOY TATTLETALE!

317
00:13:16,650 --> 00:13:19,119
JoJo: TELL ME WHAT I
SNITCHED ABOUT, THEN!

318
00:13:19,152 --> 00:13:20,286
HE'S LYING TO YOU!

319
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:22,388
WHY DO YOU
JUST TAKE HIM AT HIS WORD?!

320
00:13:22,455 --> 00:13:24,558
Boys: JOJO THE SQUEALER!

321
00:13:24,625 --> 00:13:25,391
( laughing )

322
00:13:25,458 --> 00:13:27,828
JoJo: DIO, HE'S SLANDERING ME.

323
00:13:27,894 --> 00:13:30,964
HE LIES AND LIES,
AND PEOPLE JUST EAT IT UP!

324
00:13:30,997 --> 00:13:34,901
FROM THE FIRST DAY HE SHOWED UP,
HE'S BEEN TRYING TO DESTROY ME.

325
00:13:34,968 --> 00:13:37,270
DAMN YOU, DIO BRANDO!

326
00:13:37,337 --> 00:13:42,342
DIO! DIO! DIO! DIO!

327
00:13:45,278 --> 00:13:47,447
EVER SINCE HE ARRIVED,

328
00:13:47,514 --> 00:13:49,616
EVERYONE'S TURNED ON ME,

329
00:13:49,683 --> 00:13:50,617
EVEN FATHER.

330
00:13:51,852 --> 00:13:52,819
( Danny whimpers )

331
00:13:52,853 --> 00:13:53,987
JoJo: OH, DANNY,

332
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:55,856
I KNOW YOU WILL
ALWAYS BE MY FRIEND,

333
00:13:55,956 --> 00:13:57,758
NO MATTER WHAT DIO DOES.

334
00:13:57,824 --> 00:13:59,593
( Danny whimpers )

335
00:14:00,667 --> 00:14:02,335
EH?

336
00:14:05,806 --> 00:14:07,541
HUH?

337
00:14:11,044 --> 00:14:13,379
WHO WAS THAT GIRL JUST NOW?

338
00:14:13,479 --> 00:14:16,983
I FEEL AS THOUGH
I HAVE SEEN HER FACE BEFORE.

339
00:14:17,050 --> 00:14:18,351
( gasps )

340
00:14:18,384 --> 00:14:20,787
THAT'S MY HANDKERCHIEF.

341
00:14:20,854 --> 00:14:22,388
SHE BROUGHT GRAPES.

342
00:14:22,488 --> 00:14:24,725
HEY, THANK YOU FOR THE FRUIT!

343
00:14:24,825 --> 00:14:29,195
YOU KNOW, I'LL BE HERE TOMORROW
IF YOU WANT TO COME BACK.

344
00:14:29,229 --> 00:14:30,564
( chuckles )

345
00:14:30,631 --> 00:14:34,000
DIDN'T EVEN TELL ME HER NAME.
JUST RAN AWAY.

346
00:14:34,067 --> 00:14:36,903
GIRLS ARE SUCH A CURIOUS BUNCH.

347
00:14:36,970 --> 00:14:38,171
( riders screaming )

348
00:14:38,238 --> 00:14:40,073
Narrator: A DARK TIME
IN JONATHAN'S LIFE

349
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:43,309
WAS SUDDENLY MADE BRIGHTER
BY LOVE'S GROWING EMBERS.

350
00:14:43,376 --> 00:14:45,512
THE TWO BECAME FAST FRIENDS,

351
00:14:45,579 --> 00:14:47,480
AND JONATHAN
WAS ENCHANTED BY HER.

352
00:14:47,548 --> 00:14:49,249
JoJo: ERINA PENDLETON.

353
00:14:49,349 --> 00:14:51,084
THE NAME IS MUSIC TO MY EARS.

354
00:14:51,184 --> 00:14:52,853
‐ JoJo: TAKE THIS!
‐ ( voice‐over ) SHE'S AN ANGEL.

355
00:14:54,087 --> 00:14:55,088
Erina: WHAT ON EARTH

356
00:14:55,188 --> 00:14:56,590
ARE YOU DOING TO THAT POOR TREE?

357
00:14:57,724 --> 00:15:00,601
JOJO! WHAT POSSESSED YOU
TO DO THAT?

358
00:15:00,701 --> 00:15:02,368
GOODNESS.

359
00:15:03,570 --> 00:15:06,773
JoJo: FAREWELL, ERINA,
'TIL NEXT TIME.

360
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:08,542
( Danny barks )

361
00:15:08,609 --> 00:15:10,544
♪

362
00:15:16,116 --> 00:15:18,051
( Dio chuckles )

363
00:15:18,118 --> 00:15:19,953
( Erina sighs )

364
00:15:20,053 --> 00:15:21,454
( gasps ) HUH?

365
00:15:21,522 --> 00:15:24,791
Dio: YOUR NAME WOULDN'T HAPPEN
TO BE ERINA, WOULD IT?

366
00:15:24,891 --> 00:15:28,461
YOU AND JOJO, YOU MAKE
SUCH A SMART‐LOOKING COUPLE.

367
00:15:28,529 --> 00:15:31,364
REALLY, I SHOULD HAVE
GUESSED AS MUCH.

368
00:15:31,431 --> 00:15:33,867
TRY AS I MIGHT TO RUIN HIS LIFE,

369
00:15:33,934 --> 00:15:37,270
YOUNG MASTER JONATHAN
HAS BEEN ODDLY HAPPY AS OF LATE.

370
00:15:37,303 --> 00:15:40,741
( Erina gasps )

371
00:15:43,076 --> 00:15:44,144
( gasps )

372
00:15:44,210 --> 00:15:45,812
Boys: HE‐‐HE DID IT!

373
00:15:45,879 --> 00:15:47,981
( Erina grunting )

374
00:15:48,081 --> 00:15:49,449
Boy: GIVE HER THE WHAT‐FOR!

375
00:15:49,482 --> 00:15:52,485
THE TROUBLE I'D GET INTO
IF I WERE AS BRAVE AS DIO.

376
00:15:52,586 --> 00:15:54,988
HE JUST DOES WHAT HE WANTS,
DEVIL MAY CARE.

377
00:15:55,055 --> 00:15:56,322
( Erina gasps )

378
00:15:56,389 --> 00:15:59,325
Dio: TELL ME,
HAVE YOU AND JOJO KISSED YET?

379
00:15:59,392 --> 00:16:01,502
I'LL TAKE THAT AS A NO.

380
00:16:01,602 --> 00:16:04,270
YOU THOUGHT YOUR FIRST KISS
WOULD BE JOJO,

381
00:16:04,337 --> 00:16:06,006
BUT IT WAS I, DIO.

382
00:16:06,072 --> 00:16:08,074
( Erina gasps )

383
00:16:08,141 --> 00:16:10,343
Dio: EVEN THOUGH
IT WAS BY FORCE,

384
00:16:10,410 --> 00:16:12,846
THE FACT THAT I KISSED HER
IS ENOUGH.

385
00:16:12,946 --> 00:16:15,516
I'VE KILLED THEIR ROMANCE
BEFORE IT BEGAN.

386
00:16:15,582 --> 00:16:19,352
I'LL DENY JOJO THE COMFORT
OF FRIENDSHIP AND LOVE.

387
00:16:19,452 --> 00:16:21,855
Boy: WHAT THE?
JUST LOOK AT HER, DIO.

388
00:16:21,922 --> 00:16:24,024
SHE'S TAKEN LEAVE
OF HER SENSES.

389
00:16:24,090 --> 00:16:26,026
WHAT'S WRONG WITH HER?
THAT'S DISGUSTING.

390
00:16:26,092 --> 00:16:29,195
Boy #2: WASHING OUT HER MOUTH
WITH A MUDDY PUDDLE?

391
00:16:29,262 --> 00:16:31,297
Boy #1: WHY WOULD
ANYBODY DO THAT?

392
00:16:31,364 --> 00:16:33,199
THERE'S A STREAM NOT FAR AWAY.

393
00:16:33,266 --> 00:16:34,200
( Dio scoffs )

394
00:16:34,267 --> 00:16:36,002
YOU UNGRATEFUL WENCH!

395
00:16:36,036 --> 00:16:39,439
YOU DARE SUGGEST MY KISS
IS SOMETHING TO BE WASHED OFF!

396
00:16:39,506 --> 00:16:40,874
( Erina gasps )

397
00:16:46,012 --> 00:16:48,314
Dio: COOL YOUR TEMPER,
YOU DAMNABLE FOOL.

398
00:16:48,381 --> 00:16:50,717
SHE'S NOT WORTH
LOSING YOUR HEAD OVER.

399
00:16:51,652 --> 00:16:53,386
WE'RE DONE HERE. COME ON.

400
00:16:53,486 --> 00:16:54,621
Boy #1: HUH?

401
00:16:56,222 --> 00:16:58,191
JoJo: EH? ERINA!

402
00:16:58,224 --> 00:16:59,960
HEY THERE.

403
00:17:01,067 --> 00:17:03,236
( Erina crying )

404
00:17:03,303 --> 00:17:04,237
JoJo: AHH?

405
00:17:04,304 --> 00:17:06,372
ERINA, WAIT!

406
00:17:06,406 --> 00:17:08,408
WHY'D SHE RUN OFF?

407
00:17:08,474 --> 00:17:10,176
WAS IT SOMETHING I SAID?

408
00:17:10,243 --> 00:17:12,178
( boys laughing )

409
00:17:12,245 --> 00:17:13,514
Boy #1: LOOK AT HIM, FELLAS.

410
00:17:13,580 --> 00:17:15,248
HE DOESN'T KNOW
WHY SHE RAN AWAY.

411
00:17:15,315 --> 00:17:17,083
Boy #3: WHAT DO YA SAY
WE TELL HIM?

412
00:17:17,150 --> 00:17:19,553
HE DESERVES TO KNOW WHAT
HIS PRECIOUS ERINA'S BEEN UP TO.

413
00:17:19,586 --> 00:17:21,054
Boy #1: I DUNNO.

414
00:17:21,087 --> 00:17:24,558
I'D FEEL BAD MAKING HIS
LITTLE LORDSHIP START TO CRY.

415
00:17:24,591 --> 00:17:27,093
( JoJo sputters )
THIS IS HIS DOING.

416
00:17:27,193 --> 00:17:29,262
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE, DIO?

417
00:17:29,362 --> 00:17:31,431
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE
TO MY ERINA?!

418
00:17:31,497 --> 00:17:34,768
( screams )

419
00:17:36,336 --> 00:17:39,105
DIO!

420
00:17:42,108 --> 00:17:43,409
Dio: HUSH, BOY.

421
00:17:43,443 --> 00:17:45,445
YOU WON'T SPEAK MY NAME
IN VAIN AGAIN

422
00:17:45,546 --> 00:17:47,347
IF YOU KNOW WHAT'S GOOD FOR YOU.

423
00:17:47,413 --> 00:17:48,849
Dio: WE END THIS NOW!

424
00:17:48,915 --> 00:17:51,852
I WON'T LET YOU SULLY
AN INNOCENT MAIDEN'S HONOR!

425
00:17:51,918 --> 00:17:54,555
YOUR FIGHT IS WITH ME, DAMN IT!

426
00:17:54,621 --> 00:17:55,789
Dio: UPSET ABOUT ERINA,

427
00:17:55,889 --> 00:17:57,858
THAT SHE SHARED
HER FAVORS WITH ME?

428
00:17:57,924 --> 00:17:59,893
AND NOW YOU INTEND TO GIVE ME

429
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:01,768
A PROPER THRASHING
FOR MY IMPUDENCE.

430
00:18:01,802 --> 00:18:03,970
JoJo: THIS TIME, DIO,
YOU HAVE GONE TOO FAR!

431
00:18:04,037 --> 00:18:08,274
Dio: YOU MAY BE RIGHT,
BUT YOU'RE THE ONE WHO'LL PAY!

432
00:18:08,308 --> 00:18:09,810
LOOKING TO REPEAT
YOUR PERFORMANCE

433
00:18:09,876 --> 00:18:12,813
FROM OUR BOXING MATCH?
BE MY GUEST.

434
00:18:12,913 --> 00:18:14,280
HUMPH.

435
00:18:14,314 --> 00:18:16,650
( JoJo sputters )

436
00:18:16,717 --> 00:18:19,319
I CAN'T BEAT HIM,

437
00:18:19,385 --> 00:18:21,154
BUT IF I LOSE HERE AND NOW,

438
00:18:21,254 --> 00:18:25,491
I'LL SPEND THE REST OF MY LIFE
COWERING IN DIO'S SHADOW.

439
00:18:25,592 --> 00:18:28,995
MOST OF ALL, I HAVE TO FIGHT
FOR ERINA'S HONOR.

440
00:18:29,062 --> 00:18:30,063
SHE NEEDS A CHAMPION!

441
00:18:30,130 --> 00:18:32,999
Dio: TIME TO END
THIS LITTLE PISSING MATCH.

442
00:18:33,066 --> 00:18:36,302
I'LL BEAT HIM HERE,
IN HIS OWN HOME.

443
00:18:36,336 --> 00:18:38,772
ONCE AND FOR ALL,
HE'LL KNOW HIS PROPER PLACE

444
00:18:38,839 --> 00:18:40,841
IN THIS WORLD IS UNDER MY HEEL.

445
00:18:40,907 --> 00:18:43,844
HE'LL SEE THAT IT'S USELESS
TO TRY AND DEFEAT ME.

446
00:18:43,910 --> 00:18:46,279
I SHALL BE MASTER,
NOW AND ALWAYS.

447
00:18:46,346 --> 00:18:48,014
( JoJo screaming )

448
00:18:48,114 --> 00:18:49,015
Dio: COME ON!

449
00:18:52,753 --> 00:18:55,188
PERFECT. RIGHT IN THE FACE.

450
00:18:56,623 --> 00:18:58,759
HOW ARE YOU ABLE TO GRAB ME

451
00:18:58,825 --> 00:19:00,627
AFTER SUCH A BLOW TO THE HEAD?!

452
00:19:00,694 --> 00:19:02,836
PERHAPS I WAS
TOO GENTLE WITH YOU!

453
00:19:04,538 --> 00:19:06,306
( Dio gags )

454
00:19:06,372 --> 00:19:09,676
JoJo: DIO!

455
00:19:09,710 --> 00:19:10,711
Dio: IMPOSSIBLE.

456
00:19:10,777 --> 00:19:12,145
JoJo: I'M GOING TO BEAT YOU

457
00:19:12,212 --> 00:19:14,047
‐ 'TIL YOU CRY LIKE A BABY, DIO!
‐ Dio: IMPOSSIBLE!

458
00:19:14,147 --> 00:19:17,618
HOW COULD A PAMPERED BRAT
LIKE HIM BEST ME IN A FIGHT?

459
00:19:20,153 --> 00:19:22,288
♪

460
00:19:29,395 --> 00:19:31,231
JoJo: EH?

461
00:19:31,297 --> 00:19:33,399
Dio: Y‐YOU...

462
00:19:33,466 --> 00:19:36,402
HOW‐‐HOW DARE YOU?

463
00:19:36,469 --> 00:19:39,573
BASTARD,
HOW DARE YOU STRIKE ME?!

464
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:41,742
JoJo: DIO'S CRYING.

465
00:19:41,842 --> 00:19:45,245
Dio: I'LL MAKE YOU REGRET THAT,
YOU FILTHY CUR!

466
00:19:45,345 --> 00:19:47,714
George: STOP IT, BOTH OF YOU!
THAT IS QUITE ENOUGH.

467
00:19:47,748 --> 00:19:50,050
JoJo: FATHER, I‐‐

468
00:19:51,084 --> 00:19:52,886
George: SON, I KNOW
THAT BOYS YOUR AGE

469
00:19:52,919 --> 00:19:54,187
ARE PRONE TO FISTICUFFS.

470
00:19:54,254 --> 00:19:57,423
HOWEVER, JOJO, I SAW YOU
PUMMEL DIO MERCILESSLY

471
00:19:57,490 --> 00:19:58,925
AFTER THE POINT
AT WHICH HE HAD

472
00:19:58,992 --> 00:20:00,661
OBVIOUSLY NO CHANCE
OF WINNING THE FIGHT.

473
00:20:00,727 --> 00:20:03,136
‐ SUCH IS THE MARK OF A COWARD.
‐ JoJo: FATHER!

474
00:20:03,203 --> 00:20:06,106
George: NO EXCUSES.
TO YOUR CHAMBERS, BOTH OF YOU.

475
00:20:06,172 --> 00:20:07,207
( JoJo sputters )

476
00:20:07,273 --> 00:20:10,143
George: I'LL DECIDE
YOUR PUNISHMENT ANON.

477
00:20:16,282 --> 00:20:17,383
( gardener grunts )

478
00:20:17,483 --> 00:20:19,385
HMM. THAT SEEMS STRANGE.

479
00:20:19,485 --> 00:20:21,221
WONDER WHAT'S IN THERE.

480
00:20:21,321 --> 00:20:22,388
OH, WELL.

481
00:20:22,488 --> 00:20:25,559
PROBABLY SOMETHING
A MAID THREW OUT.

482
00:20:30,063 --> 00:20:31,031
HMM?

483
00:20:31,064 --> 00:20:33,399
( thumping )

484
00:20:33,499 --> 00:20:34,635
W‐WHAT'S THAT?

485
00:20:34,701 --> 00:20:37,170
SOMETHING GOT
INTO THE INCINERATOR.

486
00:20:37,237 --> 00:20:38,705
OH, MERCY!

487
00:20:38,739 --> 00:20:40,841
WHAT‐‐WHAT IF
A PERSON'S IN THERE?

488
00:20:40,907 --> 00:20:42,576
THEY'RE BURNING ALIVE,

489
00:20:42,676 --> 00:20:45,546
AND IT'S ALL MY FAULT
FOR LIGHTING IT!

490
00:20:45,579 --> 00:20:47,748
♪

491
00:20:49,516 --> 00:20:52,052
ERINA.

492
00:20:52,085 --> 00:20:53,587
DAMN YOU, DIO!

493
00:20:53,654 --> 00:20:55,488
I BEAT YOU FAIR AND SQUARE,

494
00:20:55,556 --> 00:20:57,023
BUT WHAT DOES IT MATTER,

495
00:20:57,090 --> 00:20:59,359
IF YOU'VE RUINED THINGS
FOR ERINA AND ME?

496
00:21:03,169 --> 00:21:05,739
George: WE BURIED HIM
WHILE YOU WERE GONE, SON.

497
00:21:05,772 --> 00:21:08,008
IT WAS NOTHING
YOU SHOULD HAVE TO WITNESS.

498
00:21:08,074 --> 00:21:11,678
THE CONSTABLE SAID IT WAS
PROBABLY THE WORK OF A BURGLAR

499
00:21:11,745 --> 00:21:14,380
WHO CAUGHT SIGHT OF DANNY
AND PANICKED.

500
00:21:14,447 --> 00:21:15,381
JoJo: DIO.

501
00:21:15,448 --> 00:21:16,850
Butler: HE'S NOT HERE.

502
00:21:16,917 --> 00:21:20,353
HE HASN'T YET RETURNED
FROM SCHOOL TODAY, SIR.

503
00:21:21,622 --> 00:21:23,089
Narrator: JOJO FLED TO HIS ROOM

504
00:21:23,123 --> 00:21:25,458
AND FELL
INTO A DREAMLESS SLUMBER.

505
00:21:25,559 --> 00:21:28,529
WHEN HE AWOKE,
HE THOUGHT OF DANNY,

506
00:21:28,595 --> 00:21:30,931
HIS LOYAL PET
AND ONE TRUE FRIEND,

507
00:21:30,964 --> 00:21:34,801
NOW LOST TO HIM, AND WEPT.

508
00:21:34,868 --> 00:21:38,939
Dio: YES, I MAY HAVE EVENED
THE SCORE BY KILLING HIS MUTT,

509
00:21:38,972 --> 00:21:40,941
BUT IT DOESN'T CHANGE THE FACT

510
00:21:40,974 --> 00:21:43,243
THAT JOJO IS FAR STRONGER
THAN I'D THOUGHT.

511
00:21:43,309 --> 00:21:46,813
BLOODY HIS NOSE, AND HE
COMES BACK TWICE AS FIERCE.

512
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:49,415
MY ANGER MAKES ME VULNERABLE.

513
00:21:49,482 --> 00:21:51,384
I MUST REMEDY THAT.

514
00:21:51,451 --> 00:21:53,820
ONCE I LEARN
TO MASTER MY TEMPER,

515
00:21:53,887 --> 00:21:56,823
I'LL BE INVINCIBLE
TO THE LIKES OF JOJO.

516
00:21:56,890 --> 00:21:59,225
Narrator:
IN THE BLINK OF AN EYE,

517
